rows.label: tlk42300023_03_msg0001
rows.name:
No matter how much Avaritia develops,
the Twelve Brothersisterpon's product lineup
doesn't increase, mo!

rows.label: tlk42300023_03_msg0002
rows.name:
When I asked Motata-san, she said it would be after
the eleven siblings who went on a journey to gather
materials returned, mo.

rows.label: tlk42300023_03_msg0003
rows.name:
Invidia and Superbia... and I heard they went to
lands I've never even heard of, mo.

rows.label: tlk42300023_03_msg0004
rows.name:
But she also said that if someone doesn't go get them,
they'll surely never come back, mo.
